description: Lambert’s FoodaPalooza Mega Bus is a multi-concept Gourmet Food Truck that serves the Austin area for corporate lunches, lunch deliveries, private caterings, events & festivals. The menu options range from fancy to no-frills, and encompass a wide variety of cultures and flavors. Check it out on the street and grab a bite, or bring it to you and make your event great!
name: Levi's FoodaPalooza
